snippet.title: Dating Amber - Official Trailer | New Rom-Com exploring teenage sexuality - TNT (ch. 137) | DStv
snippet.description:
Watch Dating Amber on Monday, on 09 August at 09:30 on TNT (ch. 137) here: https://bit.ly/3A42umr.

In this rom-com set in Ireland during the mid-’90s, Eddie and Amber are two queer friends that fake a relationship to stop everyone speculating about their sexuality. Their friends can't find out about their sexual preference and moreso their parents! Eddie wants to follow his dad into the military, while Amber dreams of moving to the liberal hub of London. So whatt do they do? They date each other!
